channel.title: Guys help me
channel.description: :eek: ok i am new to makeing severs ok i have one set up all i need is to get it on online i try to regester it and it says that it is offline it says to get it on online before i should regester and another is how do i set up commands?

item.title: Guys help me
item.dc:creator: @mrdek11 mrdek11
item.description:
@mrdek11 wrote:

You can create commands by editing the “customcommand” void in client.java, there’s already some example commands in most servers, you can follow their syntax.
Also you can search google for port forwarding on your specific router.
